#. ID 1, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (18,17)
#. ID 2, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (19,17)
#. ID 3, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (17,17)
msgid "The fireflies light up this room."
msgstr "ホタルのおかげで部屋が明るいね。"

#. ID 5, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (18,13)
msgid "It's some kind of stew."
msgstr "何かのシチューみたい。"

#. ID 6, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (17,13)
msgid "Coals."
msgstr "石炭だ。"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (20,16)
msgid ""
"It's being slowly chipped away already.\n"
"But it's still trying to stay alive, \n"
"I think."
msgstr ""
"世界はゆっくりと崩壊しはじめてる。\n"
"まだ必死で生きようとしているが…"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 5, Pos (20,16)
msgid ""
"Doesn't matter... one day the world will\n"
"finally give up this fight."
msgstr ""
"だとしても…\n"
"いつか、世界があきらめる日がくるだろう。"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 7, Pos (20,16)
msgid "I just hope I'm not alive to see it."
msgstr "その日が訪れるまで、長生きしたくはないね。"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 9, Pos (20,16)
msgid ""
"I'm bringing back the sun,\n"
"though..."
msgstr "ミーが太陽を元の場所に戻すよ…"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 12, Pos (20,16)
msgid "That won't fix the root of the problem."
msgstr "けれど、根本的な問題の解決にはならない。"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 14, Pos (20,16)
msgid "Just like that other lady said... "
msgstr "あのお姉さんが言ってたことと同じだ…"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 16, Pos (20,16)
msgid ""
"But don't lose heart!\n"
"Without the sun the world will\n"
"die much faster."
msgstr ""
"だが気を落とさないでくれ!\n"
"太陽がなければ\n"
"世界はもっと早く滅びてしまうんだから。"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 19, Pos (20,16)
msgid ""
"At the very least... I'm sure\n"
"everyone would like to see the sun again."
msgstr ""
"せめて…きっとみんな、\n"
"もう一度太陽を見たいはず。"
